page.title: 14A TYPICAL SYMINGTON HOUSE
page.content: My house is detached with a back and front garden .The hall is small with a basket of peat for heating and a cupboard. In the kitchen are 10 cupboards two of them are big ones one holds dishes and the other cleaning things.There is a cooker,washing machine,sink,tumble drier and a freezer-all electric.My living room has a sofa,2 chairs and a T.V. Upstairs my mum and dad sleep in one big room with a clothes cupboard, a mirror, a five drawer chest and a bedside radio. My room has a wardrobe and a computer and T.V., a bed and a pin board full of Celtic football posters. My carpet is green. My little sisters room has two beds and a wardrobe and all her soft toys, her carpet is red. The bathroom has a bath, shower, handbasin and toilet. This is a typical house in {Symington.
